text = "Controls:
Left-click on power source to activate
Left-click on links to start placing chains
Left-click anywhere or on other links to finish placing chains
Chain \"pins\" can have two outgoing chains

Right-click to remove links or cancel chain placement
Left-click drag to pan camera
Right-click-drag to rotate camera
Scroll to zoom camera
Middle-click to reset camera rotation and zoom

Escape to quit"

